Bloody Sunday;;2002;;R;;Drama,History,War;;7.6;;Paul Greengrass;;James Nesbitt,Tim Pigott-Smith,Nicholas Farrell,Allan Gildea,Gerard Crossan,Mary Moulds,Carmel McCallion,Christopher Villiers,James Hewitt,Declan Duddy,Edel Frazer,Joanne Lindsay,Mike Edwards,Gerry Hammond,Jason Stammers,Ken Williams,Bryan Watts,Simon Mann;;Documentary-style drama showing the events that led up to the tragic incident on January 30, 1972 in the Northern Ireland town of Derry when a protest march led by civil rights activist Ivan Cooper was fired upon by British troops, killing 13 protesters and wounding 14 more.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0280491/